# Local / private Claude Code artifacts (never commit). The internal Claude
# operating files (CLAUDE.md, agents, skills, prompts, logs, cache) live here
# locally and are intentionally untracked. Only a small public-safe README.md is
# kept tracked, via the negation below. ".claude/*" (not ".claude/") is required
# so the negation can re-include the README.
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/*
!.claude/README.md
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/logs/
.claude/cache/
.claude/tmp/
.claude/agents/
.claude/skills/
